      "name": "Sky Striker Ace = Zero",
      "effect": "2 \"Sky Striker Ace\" monsters\nYou can only Special Summon \"Sky Striker Ace = Zero(s)\" once per turn. Cannot be used as Link Material. If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 \"Sky Striker\" Spell from your Deck or GY to your hand. (Quick Effect): You can Tribute this card; Special Summon both 1 \"Sky Striker Ace - Raye\" and 1 \"Sky Striker Ace - Roze\" from your Deck and/or GY, then you can destroy 1 card on the field. You can only use 1 \"Sky Striker Ace = Zero\" effect per turn, and only once that turn.",
